Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared a\Nfull day of spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been doing great,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but now it's time\Nfor a real challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is on. Where\Ndo we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Teleportation. Multiple\Nlocations. Try to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfiguration!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,SHIELDS!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo! I am on FIRE!\NWhat's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there is such a\Nthing as too much studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\NBy YayPonies\Nさよなら、『ＳＯＳ団』 ！；。；\Nhttps://yp1.yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, speed spells\Nlike Accelero are not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But if done correctly,\Nthey can allow you to be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,much more efficient\Nwith your day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go,\NStarlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not finished. I've\Ndiscovered a very old spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Similo Duplexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When combined with Accelero\Nin just the right way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can literally be\Nin two places at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,NOW I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit, your skills\Nwith magic really are
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing short of amazing.\NI'm very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been\Nsomething of a natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it doesn't\Nlook like you've tackled
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,any friendship lessons\Nsince you met Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? I\Ncould have sworn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,there were a couple\Nin there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, I'm really\Nquite busy this week...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so many commitments! I'll try\Nand find some time in my --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No time like\Nthe present!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike and I are\Nheaded to Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia wanted\Nme to give her students
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a quick overview\Non the history
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of enchanted objects\Nin Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back after the\Npresentation, which should be-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,20 moons from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight. It's a\Nquick presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Keep tellin'\Nyourself that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tackle a\Nfriendship lesson today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and we can review\Nyour progress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,when I get back\Nlater this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! No problem.\NFriendship lesson. On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Spike, help me\Ncolor code these cards
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,according to time,\Nplace and object.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Twilight and I are\Nabout to head to Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just checking to see if you\Nneed anything before we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good here. Not\Ngood. Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a problem in\Nthe world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So... what are\Nyou doing exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was... just trying to decide\Nwhich friendship lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to tackle while\Nyou two were in Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yup. Right here. Where I\Njust left them a second ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bake a cake with Pinkie Pie,\Nscrapbook with Applejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,sew with Rarity...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Help an animal with Fluttershy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,chillax with Rainbow\NDash? What is chillaxing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, uh, if\Nyou're nervous about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,your friendship lessons,\Nit's totally okay to say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,NERVOUS?! ME!\NHAHAHA. Oh Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are hilarious.\NYou think I'm nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm going to\Nfail something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as simple as baking\Na cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you were,\Nit would be--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly! Twilight just said\Nhow impressed she was
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that I combined a speed spell\Nand a duplication spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT was a challenge.\NThese? Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I could combine all five\Nof these at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,without breaking a sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think maybe you're missing--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An opportunity to\Nreally impress Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea, Spike! I'm gonna\Nget right on that. Good talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought Twilight was\Nthe master of the freakout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, with your help,\NI figure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,these should be\Ndone in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is what\NTwilight would want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you might\Nwanna take your time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with each of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But by working as a team,\Nwe can get them done faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And isn't teamwork a key\Nfactor in friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Super! Pinkie Pie,\Nsince we're baking,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be in\Nthe kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, Applejack you two\Ncan set up in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know that\Nthe dusty old library
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,has the proper lighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we can stay\Nout here in the foyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that Fluttershy and\NI could work with the animals
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,right here in the foyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, whatever\Nyou think is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Now, Rainbow Dash--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it might depend{\i0}\N{\i1} on the animal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, this poor little\Neagle with a sprained wing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,might be better off up\Nin one of the towers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And these adorable chipmunks\Nmight prefer a nook somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you spent\Nsome time getting to-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In a minute, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't know if we\Ncan chillax properly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in the castle. We need\Nvery specific conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,for optimal chillaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I just assumed chillaxing\Ncould happen anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. Shows what you know\Nabout chillaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do some\Nlocation scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,O-kay. Uh, it seemed\Nmore efficient to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,start with the scrapbooking\Nso we could just get it out--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh! oh!\NCan we start with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna need time for the\Ncake to bake! After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ It's a piece of cake{\i0}\N{\i1} to bake a pretty cake-- ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, we're on a schedule.\NNo time for a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We can start with\Nbaking. THEN--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't design dresses\Nafter you've been baking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,with Pinkie. She\Ncan be a bit messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. We can start with\Nthe dresses and THEN--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,While y'all figure that out,\NI'm gonna start layin out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the pictures for scrapbooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a whole\Nlot of time to cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is a whole lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got at least 80\Nmoons worth of memories
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to go through!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,80 moons!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There is NOwhere to\Nchillax in this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have to\Nset up somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you all excuse\Nme for one second?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. That pony really\Nneeds to chillax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, Starlight.\NYou've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A handful of friendship\Nlessons is nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,compared to the spells\Nyou've mastered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I cast a little\Nspell to help things along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Something simple and\Nsafe. Fiducia Compelus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not bad. They\Nwould barely notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Cogeria so they are\Nmore open to suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe Cogeria combined\Nwith Fiducia Compelus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... that could work nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, with a hint of Persuadere\Nto be sure it sticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony will\Nprobably thank me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,for getting it all\Ndone so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And Twilight will\Nbe thrilled
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've completed so many\Nlessons. Everypony wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations Starlight,\Nyou're a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the congratulations\Nwere a little premature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cogeria...\NPersuadere...Fiducia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course! Fiducia\NCompelus needs a trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,PONIES! HEAR MY\NVOICE AND LISTEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, kitchen. Rarity,\NApplejack, library.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, find\Nsomewhere INSIDE the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and set up a place\Nwhere we can chillax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to work, Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okie-Dokie. What would\Nyou like to do first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. What are we\Nsupposed to do first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want to do\Nfirst, Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In a medium-sized\Nmixing bowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,beat together eggs, sugar and\Ntwo teaspoons of vanilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mix in flour...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Add baking soda,\Nsalt and cinnamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you can\Ntake it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take what from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The baking. Just keep\Nfollowing the instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in the book until I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Absotively!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Instruction following starting... NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Baking a cake, check!\NNow on to sewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you have\Nin mind, Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want me to have\Nin my mind, Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make a dress\Nexactly like that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,JUST like this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely! It will\Nlook perfectly divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a whole\Nlot of photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you usually\Norganize them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However you want me to\Norganize them, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. Tell me\Nabout this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet Apple Acres.\N20 moons ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith was looking\Nfor her favorite pie tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked in the kitchen,\Nbut it wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked in the barn,\Nbut it wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need every\Nlittle detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sum up the story\Nin one sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Turns out Granny\NSmith didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,HOW to make a pig\Ndo the backstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Why don't you\Nkeep putting these photos
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in chronological order\Nand when I come back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you can give me\Nmore highlights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing,\NStarlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy? Where\Nare all the animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And why didn't\Nyou stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you\Ndidn't ask me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously I wanted\Nyou to-- never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please round up all\Nthe animals in the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring them back\Nhere to the foyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All the animals. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find a place to\Nchillax, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing,\NStarlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Let me know\Nwhen it's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Starlight Glimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith knew she was\Ngonna need a bigger boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So Goldie Delicious says, "If\Nyou can't say anything nice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,about anypony...\Ncome sit by me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mac knew if he just\Ncovered himself in mud,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the creature wouldn't\Nbe able to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer!\NI have finished the dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it gorgeous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted me\Nto make a dress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly like the\None in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go make a REAL\Ndress out of fabric
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly like the\None in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh. I see. Yes, of\Ncourse, Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! Make it BIGGER\Nthan the one in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, darling.\NBigger it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just a pony, standing\Nin front of another pony,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,asking him to love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Following all of the\Ninstructions in the cookbook
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in order, Starlight Glimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant just the ONE cake! I\Nwas only gone a few minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How in Equestria did you get\Nall of this done so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,First I combined\Nthree eggs, then--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the baking\Nlesson is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They can take our farm, but\Nthey can't take our freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gathered all of the\Nanimals like you asked,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, this will do\Nnicely. A MUCH bigger dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the best\Nof apples;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it was the worst\Nof apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle this. It's just\Nmagic and I know magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The cakes are burning!\NYou left the ovens on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We need water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Storm clouds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mac told me, with\Na whole lotta power
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,comes a heckuva lot\Nof responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't get any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT IS GOING ON!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea we had\Nspiders in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never sleeping again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I had reversed the\NFiducia Compelus and Cogeria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I added\Ntoo much Persuadere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really missing\Nthe point here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally untangled\Nthat mess of a spell
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and got everypony home. It\Nwas really powerful stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna feel\Nthat in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please try to\Nexplain to me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,how in the name\Nof Celestia
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,things got this\Nout of control?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was the first time\NI cast that particular spell
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't fully\Nthink it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet if I had reversed--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you might be\Nmissing the point here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Told ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you think\Nthat casting a spell
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,on your friends\Nto do your bidding
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,was even remotely\Na good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you put it that\Nway, it sounds really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because it\NIS really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight. I'm not mad at\Nyou. But I am disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been doing so well.\NI just don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,how a friendship lesson\Nturned into all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been avoiding the\Nfriendship lessons on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can cast complex spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But baking a cake with\NPinkie Pie freaks me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And yes I know how\Nridiculous that sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't\Nsay anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I just\Nkept wowing you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with my magical abilities,\Nyou might just... not notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Baking a cake\Nfreaks you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Baking a cake,\Nsewing. All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I was\Nbad at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to be a\Ndisappointment to anypony
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I ended up being a\Ndisappointment to everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight. Do you\Nthink anypony cares
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can bake a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But the lesson--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Was to get to know\NPinkie Pie better
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,by doing something\Nshe loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a friendship lesson,\Nnot a baking lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You know I think I might\Nhave missed the point here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Told ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for a pretty\Nadvanced friendship lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno what kinda whammy\NStarlight put on us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but I feel like I got\Nshoved through the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Speedy Cider\NSqueezy 6000™.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If everypony could speak in a\Nwhisper for the next few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be delightful.\NMy head is thumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was up all night\Ncalming the animals down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, please!\NNot so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight's spell made me\Nburn perfectly good cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I NEVER burn cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, about that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Things got a little\Nout of hand last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that the\Nunderstatement of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell it to the cakes, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we all PLEASE argue\Nat a lower volume?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I really messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast the spell because I was\Nnervous about working with you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,on the friendship lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here's a friendship\Nlesson for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cast spells\Non your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me; I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did was wrong and\NI can't take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right to be upset\Nand I hope one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make it up to you. But\Nall I can say is I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you'll excuse me, I've\Ngot to go clean the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,covered in wet cake\Nbatter and spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a pretty\Ngood apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like she\Nfeels really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Starlight! Most of\Nthe Apple family photos
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are still laying\Naround in the wreckage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll come along\Nand hunt 'em down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! And I feel awful for\Ndisturbing all of those
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,cute little spiders and\Nbats. I should check on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. And I left\Nsome lovely fabric out;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I should come move it to\Nthat nice quiet library.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'll come and get\Nthose storm clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Somepony has to\Nbake a cake to honor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the poor cakes that\Nsacrificed their batter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in last night's tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems your\Napology went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just lucky to have\Nsuch understanding friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's probably\Ngoing to be a while
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,before I try to tackle those\Nfriendship lessons again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? You've\Nbeen doing them all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been cleaning\Nup the mess I made
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,by totally failing\Nat friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? But didn't I see\Nyou sewing with Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes but--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you and Applejack did\Na great job collecting
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,those photos and putting\Nthem in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping animals with Fluttershy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,baking with Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Those sound like your\Nassignments to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I think there's just\None that you're missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun? Check. Chairs? Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks to a simple\Ncatadupa levitata spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we've got water! Is that\Neverything we need to chillax?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No? What did I miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've completed\Nanother friendship lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! She completes the lesson\Nwhen I say she completes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So less learning\Nand more chillaxing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how long do we\Nsit quietly?
